Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.88,0:15:17.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托  快醒醒\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Come on, wake up, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.15,0:15:19.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们必须赶紧离开这儿  在\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}We gotta get out of here before--
