Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.17,0:15:38.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来啊  让我看看你的本事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}So go ahead, Give me what you got.
