Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.16,0:15:59.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没事吧  发生什么事了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Are you all right? what happened?
