Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.37,0:16:15.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是我之前所说的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}This is what I was talking about.
