Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.66,0:16:34.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真不敢相信暑假就要结束了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I just can't believe the summer's almost over.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.23,0:16:37.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在我知道了高中生活是多么的糟糕\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}And now that I know how awful high school's gonna be,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.87,0:16:40.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不急着要开始经历那场人生悲剧了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I'm in no hurry to start that train wreck.
