Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.90,0:16:44.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过年龄的增长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}But just because you're growing up
