Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.74,0:16:52.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我不想和重力泉告别\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}But I don't want to say good-bye to Gravity Falls.
