Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.99,0:16:58.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赴汤蹈火  在所不辞\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}through thick and thin.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.12,0:17:00.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是每个人都能有那种体验  你知道么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Not everyone can say that, you know.
