Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.73,0:17:09.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我总是有迪普相伴\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I always have Dipper.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.20,0:17:11.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个小可爱  我的小依靠\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Good old reliable old...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.03,0:17:12.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还好吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Are you okay?
