Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.17,0:17:21.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也包括你和我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}And that includes you and me.
