Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.62,0:17:26.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和我一起留下来吧  迪普\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Stay here with me, Dipper.
