Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.95,0:17:34.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我答应你  我会留下来的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I'll do it. I'm gonna stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.22,0:17:35.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好极了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Excellent.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.82,0:17:38.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在  谁想去拯救世界  乖徒弟\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Now, who wants to save the world, apprentice?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.07,0:17:48.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梅宝  我刚刚经历了生命中最棒的一天\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Mabel, I just had the best day of my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.37,0:17:50.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,飞碟是真实存在的  镇子下面就有一个\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}UFOs are real, and there's one under the town,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.81,0:17:53.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还救了阿福叔公  而且\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}and I saved Great Uncle Ford's life and--
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.01,0:17:54.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿  你还好吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Hey, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.84,0:17:56.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告诉我这不是真的  迪普\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Tell me it's not true, Dipper.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.84,0:17:58.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告诉我你是在开玩笑\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Tell me you were joking.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.88,0:18:03.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿福的徒弟  你是认真的吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Ford's apprentice? Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.12,0:18:05.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听着  我只是在考虑  而且这事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Look, I was thinking, and this is
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.85,0:18:07.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对我来说是个大好机会\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}a huge opportunity for me.
