Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.16,0:18:21.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而现在你也要离开我了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}and now you're leaving me, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.84,0:18:23.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听我说  这事我考虑过\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Look, I've been thinking about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.61,0:18:25.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我又不是要永远离开  好吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I won't be gone forever, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.34,0:18:26.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还是会回家看你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I'll still visit you at home
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.57,0:18:28.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们能在网上聊天  这事是可以解决的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}and we'll chat online-- we'll make it work.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.84,0:18:30.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想解决这事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I don't want it to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.99,0:18:33.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就想让这个暑假永远持续下去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I just wish summer could last forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.21,0:18:35.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但这不可能  梅宝\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}But it can't, Mabel.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.15,0:18:38.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听着  世界不可能永远定格在这一刻\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Look, things aren't gonna stay frozen this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.22,0:18:39.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是成长的一部分\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}It's part of growing up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.89,0:18:41.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,势不可挡\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Things change.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.29,0:18:43.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,寒来暑往\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Summer ends.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.06,0:18:46.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梅宝  等等\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Mabel, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.19,0:18:48.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是那个意思\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I didn't mean it like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.33,0:18:50.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梅宝  快回来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Mabel, come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.11,0:19:03.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在只有聚会巧克力能让我高兴点儿了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Only party chocolate can cheer me up now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.14,0:19:06.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宅男图书  被啃过的笔  \N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Nerd books? Chewed up pens?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.01,0:19:08.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噢  拿错了包\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Ugh, wrong backpack.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.28,0:19:10.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不公平\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}It's not fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.08,0:19:13.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只希望暑假永不结束\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I just wish summer could last forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.05,0:19:15.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说不定有可能\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}That might be possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.42,0:19:18.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毛衣城现在拒接电话\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Sweater Town is not accepting incoming calls right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.89,0:19:20.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梅  梅  梅宝  是我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}M-M-Mabel, it's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.30,0:19:23.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么  谁在说话\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}What? Who said that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.06,0:19:25.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能帮助你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I can help.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.23,0:19:27.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个时间旅行的家伙\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}The time travel guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.44,0:19:29.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在这里干嘛呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.38,0:19:31.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说你不想让暑假结束  对吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}You said you don't want summer to end, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.47,0:19:33.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没听错吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Did I hear that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.25,0:19:34.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.18,0:19:35.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要这么问\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Why are you asking?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.58,0:19:37.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听着  虽然这可能违反规定\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Look, maybe it's against the rules,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.54,0:19:39.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是你曾经帮助过我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}but you once did a favor for me, so
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.31,0:19:40.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我觉得应该回报你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I thought I could help you out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.46,0:19:41.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有一种时间泡泡\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}It's called a time bubble,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.84,0:19:43.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它能阻止时光流逝\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}and it prevents time from going forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.80,0:19:46.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在重力泉的暑假  你想要多久就有多久\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Summer in Gravity Falls can last as long as you want it to.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.79,0:19:50.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗  这东西怎么用\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Really? But how does it work.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.66,0:19:53.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只需要你到你叔公那里给我拿个小玩意儿\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I just need you to get a little gizmo for me from your uncle.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.53,0:19:55.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是个小东西  他都不会发现它不见了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Something small-- he won't even know it's missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.80,0:19:59.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许迪普的呆子袋里会有那种东西\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Huh, maybe Dipper has something like that in his nerd bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.43,0:20:03.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我猜猜  梅宝无法坦然接受吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Let me guess. Mabel didn't take it well?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.67,0:20:05.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我  我不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I--I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.41,0:20:07.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许我在做错误的决定  \N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Maybe I'm making the wrong decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.61,0:20:09.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我得好好考虑这件事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I need to think about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.08,0:20:11.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迪普  我们现在应该集中精力在任务上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Dipper, right now we need to focus on the mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.91,0:20:13.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧  我把粘合剂拿来了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Now, come on. I've got the glue.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.58,0:20:15.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把裂痕给我  让我们史册留名\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Hand me the rift and let's make history.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.58,0:20:19.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.39,0:20:21.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  裂痕\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Oh, no, the rift!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.59,0:20:24.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好奇怪啊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Huh. That's odd.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.83,0:20:26.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这个吗  对  就是这个\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Is this it? Yes, that's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.93,0:20:29.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快给我  我好来帮你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Just hand it over and I'll do my thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.46,0:20:32.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除非你准备离开重力泉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Unless you're ready to leave Gravity Falls.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.40,0:20:35.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要夏天长一点点就行\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Just a little more summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.61,0:20:42.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.62,0:20:50.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  等等  等等  等一下\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Oh, no! Wait, wait, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.39,0:20:57.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不容易啊  总算成了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}At last. At long, long last!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.93,0:21:00.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两个世界之间的门开啦\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}The gate between worlds is open!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.49,0:21:03.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,十亿年前预言的大事件要来啦\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}The event one billion years prophesized has come to pass!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.90,0:21:07.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等到这一天啦  这个世界终于是我的啦\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}The day has come. The world is finally mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.42,0:21:24.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发生了什么事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.69,0:21:26.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.62,0:21:29.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们迟了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}We're too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.22,0:21:31.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世界末日到了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}It's the end of the world.
